{"tid":1604540,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"全世界入黎 今晚同我寫封家書","createTime":"2019-09-30T03:57:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T15:27:12.000Z","uid":264281,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"285fa776c5c908b7249606d35ba84373263d83e3","tid":1604540,"uid":264281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:57:23.000Z","msg":"聽日出門前send俾屋企人<br />\n伴侶 好朋友 或者你有野想同佢講嘅人<br />\n<br />\n以自己為例 平時好多野都唔會講出口<br />\n翻到屋企又會好任性唔理人(利申:家人深藍)<br />\n我知道咁多年黎 無論發生咩事 就算政治立場唔同都好<br />\n屋企人都會默默地守護喺身邊 盡能力去保護我<br />\n所以為左屋企人 我甘願意付出所有<br />\n<br />\n希望藉呢個機會<br />\n將平時講唔出口嘅說話寫低晒佢<br />\n寫信有時係容易過講出口百萬倍<br />\n<br />\n家書並無特別格式<br />\n只要坦誠 講出心底話<br />\n感謝 道歉 表白 都可<br />\n唔好俾自己有遺憾<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n願榮光歸香港<br />\n十一見"},{"pid":"c54ba97b545cb39e2bda3344cecbc489f4abad82","tid":1604540,"uid":182088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:06:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a21e52b1c412db29b6578cf7138e99a34f65b40f","tid":1604540,"uid":64469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:12:52.000Z","msg":"［十一］暴風雨前夕 文宣組做野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1604081\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1604081</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d5dc65d0bbbaf9e4c5303fc244724345e2e637d1","tid":1604540,"uid":203332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:14:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b8cdf7191cf6e6a79eae629ba81991320e61d391","tid":1604540,"uid":183332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:25:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f64d014843420bb011e79a40705bba83767ad433","tid":1604540,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:27:12.000Z","msg":"有野想捐可以FB搵我地香港自由之書阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"